


	
        Watching the game of Telephone play out in five seconds          Raymond Chen        
            
            November 26th, 20100 0
		
        Some time ago, I spent the Thanksgiving holiday with my nieces (ages 3 and 5 at the time), and I overheard this conversation between them.
 “Thanksgiving is over.”
 — Christmas is coming!
 “It’s Christmas time!”
 — Today is Christmas! 

        
                

        
		
                

            
            
                
